title: Trailer Park Boys Soundtrack Collection
description:
My collection of music from and inspired by the Trailer Park Boys. 
It's as complete as I could come up with, but I'm sure there's plenty missing. Still, this is like striking gold for any real fan of the show.

Includes music from 7 seasons, Big Dirty, Liqour Day, Bubbles and J-Roc originals, fanmade, a few other lost gems (like the full length version of the commercial on the radio when Bubbles is getting high during the meat stealing operation)

Enjoy!
